      "text": [
        " اَلْمَحْصُورِ وَ لَمْ يَسُقِ اَلْهَدْيَ قَالَ «يَنْسُكُ وَ يَرْجِعُ» قِيلَ فَإِنْ لَمْ يَجِدْ هَدْياً قَالَ «يَصُومُ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3106 - Muawiyah ibn Ammar narrated from Abu Abdullah (as) regarding the Mahsur (prevented) who did not bring a sacrificial animal.\nImam (as) said: \"He performs his rites and returns.\"\nIt was asked: \"What if he cannot find a sacrificial animal?\"\nImam (as) said: \"He should fast.\""
        ]
      }
    },
